reviewText: My twins love Barney, they were so excited to get her new a DVD since they lost the old one. No scratches and played great. Thank You
A great purchase - we received the dvd in a timely manner, and product is as exactly as described

2 of the 3 DVD's were not so good for younger viewers.  Concepts and format were more for 2 - 4 year's.  For littlies, stick with Barney's House (the Best), Lets go to the Zoo, Barney's Beach Party and Barney Fun and Games etc.

The jungle adventure part of the Land of Make Believe is very good, linking animals to parts of the song.  Weseem to enjoy that particularly.
